    • removePadding

      static String[] removePadding​(String[] pattern)
      Removes empty space from around the recipe pattern.

      Turns patterns such as:

       
 "   o"
 "   a"
 "    "
      Into: 
       
 "o"
 "a"
      Returns:
      a new recipe pattern with all leading and trailing empty rows/columns removed
